#- So you are interested in Crimburg property, then, eh? Good choice. Crimburg is a wonderful place for a permanent residence or simply a vacation home. Regardless, you'll like it here.
  At any given time, several apartments will be availible, price 
#- varrying. If you see one you like, contact Zdorab to purchase. Once you own the property, you agree to use it in the ways outlined in the rules and regulations seen to the left of this shelf. (and up one.) I hope you buy an apartment, not for my sake, but
#- so you can enjoy all the wonderful Crimburg perks!
